    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We included 852 patients in a prospectively recruiting multicenter matched case-control study in Germany to assess vaccine effectiveness (VE) in preventing COVID-19-associated hospitalization (Delta-variant dominance). Two-dose VE was 89% (95%CI 84-93%) overall, 79% in patients with &gt;2 comorbidities and 77% in adults aged 60-75 years. A third dose increased VE to &gt;93% in all patient-subgroups.</jats:p>",
